---
title: Cheat's Ciabatta Pizzas with Smokey Homemade Salsa and Fresh Basil
description: Quick, easy and delicious, Patrick's simple 'cheat's ciabatta pizzas are the perfect thing to knock together when you're a little short of time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/550849896ced6efa2e8b457c.jpg
